    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>to a heatproof bowl</p><p>Cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until the squash cubes are fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663689469766-x200.jpg",
