          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1663689486814-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1663689486814-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1663689486814-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spinach & ricotta ravioli & kale</strong> to the pan and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your<strong> ricotta & butternut squash sauce with spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong></p><p>Tip: Add an extra splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little thick</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1663689491480-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
